OL,3,CSouth West Water to pay #24m over
OL,4,Csewage failures
OL,6,FSouth West Water will have to spend
OL,7,F#24 million to improve the region's
OL,8,Fwater infrastructure after the
OL,9,Findustry regulator found failures in
OL,10,Fthe maintenance and operations of its
OL,11,Fsewage and water network.
OL,13,FOfwat found the company had failed to
OL,14,Fmeet its legal obligations in managing
OL,15,Fits wastewater treatment works and
OL,16,Fnetwork, which resulted in the company
OL,17,Fspilling sewage into the environment.
