OL,3,CSouth West Water to pay #24m over
OL,4,Csewage failures
OL,6,FIt's part of the water regulator's
OL,7,Flargest investigation into the
OL,8,Fperformance of water companies, which
OL,9,Fhas already seen Yorkshire Water,
OL,10,FThames Water, and Northumbrian Water
OL,11,Ffined a total of more than #160m.
OL,13,FSouth West Water said it has proposed
OL,14,Fto invest the "enforcement package" in
OL,15,Flocal nature recovery projects and
OL,16,Fimprovements to the region's water
OL,17,Finfrastructure.
OL,19,FThe proposal will now go to a public
OL,20,Fconsultation before Ofwat makes its
OL,21,Ffinal decision.
