OL,3,CSouth West Water to pay #24m over
OL,4,Csewage failures
OL,6,FLynn Parker, Senior Director for
OL,7,FEnforcement at Ofwat, said: "Water
OL,8,Fcompanies should be in no doubt that
OL,9,Fthey will be held to account if they
OL,10,Ffail to meet their legal obligations
OL,11,Fto customers and the environment.
OL,13,F"Our investigation found a range of
OL,14,Ffailures in how South West Water has
OL,15,Fgone about managing its wastewater
OL,16,Fbusiness. That is why we have secured
OL,17,Fthe #24m package and a commitment to
OL,18,Fput things right.
