OL,3,CSouth West Water to pay #24m over
OL,4,Csewage failures
OL,6,F"As we continue to progress our sector-
OL,7,Fwide investigation, we are pleased
OL,8,Fthat companies like South West Water
OL,9,Fare stepping up to acknowledge their
OL,10,Ffailures and to put things right. We
OL,11,Fwill continue to monitor the company
OL,12,Fto ensure that this work is carried
OL,13,Fout as quickly as possible so that
OL,14,Fcustomer confidence can begin to be
OL,15,Frestored."
OL,17,FSouth West Water CEO, Susan Davy,
OL,18,Fsaid: "We are pleased that Ofwat has
OL,19,Fcompleted its review into wastewater
OL,20,Fat South West Water as part of its
OL,21,Fsector wide investigation.
