OL,3,CSouth West Water to pay #24m over
OL,4,Csewage failures
OL,6,F"For South West Water this related to
OL,7,Fhistorical issues. I have always said
OL,8,Fthat when things go wrong, it is how
OL,9,Fwe respond and put things right and
OL,10,Fthat is exactly what we are doing.
OL,12,F"In response to Ofwat's findings, we
OL,13,Fhave proposed a ringfenced investment
OL,14,Fprogramme of #24m to spend more to
OL,15,Ffurther reduce spills, tackle sewer
OL,16,Fmisuse and establish a Nature Recovery
OL,17,FFund, benefiting environmental groups
OL,18,Fin Devon and Cornwall and the wider
OL,19,Fcommunity.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
