OL,3,CSouth West Water to pay #24m over
OL,4,Csewage failures
OL,6,F"his is in addition to the #760m we
OL,7,Fare already investing over the next 5
OL,8,Fyears to reduce the use of storm
OL,9,Foverflows across the region."
OL,11,FOfwat added South West Water has taken
OL,12,Fsome steps to address its compliance
OL,13,Fissues. These include investment to
OL,14,Finvestigate and improve the operation
OL,15,Fof a range of its treatment works and
OL,16,Fstorm overflows, and the introduction
OL,17,Fof new governance arrangements to
OL,18,Fensure greater oversight of its
OL,19,Fcompliance with its environmental
OL,20,Fobligations.
